commit c831efd6fc895f98595c4cf2a40470eda8a66b56
Author: Thomas Müller <git@tom94.net>
Date:   Sun Feb 22 08:47:50 2026 +0100

    feat(dng): CFA demosaicing

    Splits up DNG postprocessing into steps that have to happen before
    demosaicing and steps that have to happen after. Also fixes the behavior
    of some of these steps (like handling rational black levels correctly &
    applying white balance w.r.t. asshotneutral metadata).

    The demosaicing has two pathways: a high-quality pathway for bayer
    filters using librtprocess and a low-quality, but general pathway for
    arbitrary patterns (vibe coded).
